{
  "stem": "3382.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I, I asked my-- and I decided to make a doctorate.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I asked my professor to accept me as a assistant in department, which was quite unusual that-- because geographers had a tacit understanding among themselves in Poland not to take minorities as assistants because of the trouble in Lemberg, in Lwow-- who was one of the Ukrainian Kubiyovych, Volodymyr Kubiyovych.",
      "word_count": 51
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Brilliant man, really brilliant, maybe more brilliant than any one of young Polish geographers, because when he graduated, he got his PhD.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So he started to write against Poles and support-- we was-- he was Ukrainian, Ukrainian nationalism.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So since then, his professor, the famous-- world-famous Romer and others, made it-- no minorities on the National Chair of Geography.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And believe me, there were at least two brilliant-- probably more brilliant-- men than I was.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "One was Zdislaw Simcher, who graduated Cracow.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And one was Josef Haliczer, who graduated [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Lwow or Lemberg.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they never were accepted and never permitted to publish even in [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Polish geographical magazines.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were two Jewish.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But I-- was one very, very good friend of mine.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Simcher perished during the Holocaust.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't know exactly how.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And Professor Haliczer, under an assumed name, survived.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we met a couple times.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We knew each other before the war.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We met.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I still have his books in our upstairs, in my study, whatever or not.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was married in 1936, after I-- in April or May, I got my master's diploma.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I got accepted as a assistant.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] At the very same time, the high school Tarbut, the Hebrew-- Hebrew high school, asked me to teach geography.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because they tried to get so-called state rights.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
